'''Vibro maces''' were large, heavy maces incorporating [[Vibro-ax/Legends|vibro-ax]] technology. They were often used by large [[Neimoidian/Legends|Neimoidian]] [[Neimoidian Gunnery Battalion|brutes]]. However, they were very slow and difficult to handle.

